		        <tr>
			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerBioLabel">Richard Dansky is the manager of design for Red Storm Entertainment and the Central Clancy Writer for Ubisoft. Richard has designed, written for or otherwise contributed to numerous games, including Far Cry: Instincts, Rainbow Six: 3 and the award-winning Ghost Recon: Island Thunder. Richard is the author of four novels, including “Chosen of the Sun” and numerous articles and pieces of short fiction. He also spent four years working for White Wolf Game Studios, where he helped design and write over 120 role-playing game books, including “Wraith: The Oblivion 2nd Edition,” “Vampire: The Masquerade Revised,” and “Laws of the Night.”</span></td>
